bill.summary:
12/6/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the suspension of duty on Glycine, N,N-BisY2-hydroxy-3-(2-propenyloxy)propyl?-, monosodium salt, reaction products with ammonium hydroxide and pentafluoroiodoethane-tetrafluoroethylyene telomer.
